com.apple.eawt.event
Class GestureEvent

java.lang.Object
  com.apple.eawt.event.GestureEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
GesturePhaseEvent, MagnificationEvent, RotationEvent, SwipeEvent
public abstract class GestureEvent
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract event all gestures inherit from. Note: GestureEvent is not subclass of AWTEvent and is not dispatched directly from the EventQueue. This is an intentional design decision to prevent collision with an official java.awt.* gesture event types subclassing InputEvent. GestureListeners are only notified from the AWT Event Dispatch thread.

Since:
Java for Mac OS X 10.5 Update 7, Java for Mac OS X 10.6 Update 2
See Also:
GestureUtilities
